# MCP Server Configuration for ChatGPT Integration

## Custom MCP Server for Guitar Marketplace

This file contains the complete implementation of a custom MCP server designed to integrate our German guitar marketplace data with ChatGPT and other AI systems.

## MCP Server Implementation

